snippet.title: AMBER HEARD - LIFESTYLE AND NET WORTH
snippet.description:
In today's video, join us as we show you the lifestyle and net worth of Amber Heard. Behind all the drama and issues she has faced, Amber Heard remains to be one of the highest paid women in Hollywood. Amber Heard is an American actress who is known for playing her role as Mera in the Justice League series. Aside from this, she has also starred in different TV shows, and that is why she has a huge amount of net worth.

Currently, Amber Heard is facing a huge and serious legal battle focusing around her and her ex-husband Johnny Depp’s abuse accusations. But before this, let’s look back at the lifestyle of Amber Heard and how she has earned her current net worth. Make sure to watch the whole video and see the successful life of Amber Heard!
